-- China Relocates 60,886 People for Water-Diversion Project, Xinhua Reports
-- Joshua Fellman
-- 2010-09-20T19:33:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-20/china-relocates-60-886-people-for-water-diversion-project-xinhua-reports.html

          
          
             China has resettled about 60,886
residents from 57 villages in the central province of Henan to
make way for a south-to-north water diversion project, Xinhua
News Agency said, citing an arm of the Cabinet.  
 The people, from Xichuan county, were moved to 63 sites in
25 other counties in the province, Xinhua said, citing the State
Councilâ€™s South-to-North Water Diversion Office. The project
will divert water from the Yangtze to Beijing and other northern
cities, the news agency said.  
          
          


  


        